@startuml
title Подсистема /v1/ask (LLM-ответ по результатам поиска)

actor "Клиент системы" as Client
participant "FastAPI\nPOST /v1/ask" as API
participant "SearchService\nanswer_from_search_items" as Service
participant "LLMService\nanswer_from_items" as LLM
participant "Ollama API\n/api/generate" as Ollama

Client -> API: POST /v1/ask {question, items[]}

alt items пустой
  API --> Client: 422 Unprocessable Entity
  return
end

API -> Service: answer_from_search_items(question, items)
Service -> LLM: answer_from_items(question, items)

LLM -> LLM: sort items by score desc
LLM -> LLM: build context JSON\n(core payload + compact graph)
LLM -> LLM: build data schema JSON\n(domain_schema + observed fields)
LLM -> LLM: render prompt from mustache template\n(question, context, data_schema, allowed_ids)

LLM -> Ollama: POST /api/generate\n{model, prompt, stream=false, temperature}
Ollama --> LLM: response text

LLM -> LLM: postprocess:\nextract <think>\nstrip think from answer\ntry parse JSON answer\nfallback to plain text
LLM --> Service: {answer, think}
Service --> API: {answer, think}

API -> Service: get_llm_model()
Service --> API: model
API -> Service: resolve_used_context_items(len(items))
Service --> API: used_items

API --> Client: 200 AskResponse\n{request_id, answer, think, model, used_items}

alt LLMServiceError
  Service --> API: error
  API --> Client: 502 Bad Gateway
end

@enduml
